00:01:18.890 --> 00:01:22.890
and desirous of serving Jehovah fully.

00:01:22.890 --> 00:01:25.890
And we appreciate that.

00:01:25.890 --> 00:01:29.890
How is it that you young men

00:01:29.890 --> 00:01:31.890
can be spiritually strong

00:01:31.890 --> 00:01:34.890
and demonstrate your heartfelt appreciation

00:01:34.890 --> 00:01:36.890
