00:02:23.830 --> 00:02:26.830
that is, Jehovah's Word, proved true,

00:02:26.830 --> 00:02:31.830
the saying of Jehovah is what refined him.

00:02:31.830 --> 00:02:37.830
So how did the saying of Jehovah refine Joseph?

00:02:37.830 --> 00:02:39.830
We know that as a young man,

00:02:39.830 --> 00:02:41.830
Joseph was gifted by Jehovah

00:02:41.830 --> 00:02:45.830
with dreams that had prophetic significance.

00:02:45.830 --> 00:02:49.530
The dreams indicated that Joseph

00:02:49.530 --> 00:02:52.530
would enjoy some wonderful privileges.

00:02:52.530 --> 00:02:55.530
But in fact, it would be years

00:02:55.530 --> 00:03:00.530
before Jehovah's promise would be realized.

00:03:00.530 --> 00:03:02.530
And in those intervening years,

00:03:02.530 --> 00:03:04.530
as verse 18 indicates,

00:03:04.530 --> 00:03:09.530
Joseph went through some very challenging times.

00:03:09.530 --> 00:03:12.530
How did he remain faithful?

00:03:12.530 --> 00:03:15.530
Well, he knew Jehovah.

00:03:15.530 --> 00:03:18.530
And rather than drawing away from Jehovah,

00:03:18.530 --> 00:03:21.530
he drew closer to Jehovah

00:03:21.530 --> 00:03:23.530
with full faith that Jehovah

00:03:23.530 --> 00:03:25.530
would keep his promise.

00:03:25.530 --> 00:03:29.530
As a result, the experiences refined him.

00:03:29.530 --> 00:03:33.530
And when it was Jehovah's time,

00:03:33.530 --> 00:03:38.530
Joseph qualified for some amazing privileges.

00:03:38.530 --> 00:03:43.530
Now, what can you young men learn from Joseph's example?

00:03:43.530 --> 00:03:46.530
Don't rush a privilege.

00:03:46.530 --> 00:03:49.530
Be patient, willing to wait on Jehovah

00:03:49.530 --> 00:03:53.530
and learn what he's teaching you today.

00:03:53.530 --> 00:03:56.530
And if you take that approach,

00:03:56.530 --> 00:03:59.530
you will be loyal to Jehovah

00:03:59.530 --> 00:04:02.530
and just as Jehovah was loyal to Joseph,

00:04:02.530 --> 00:04:05.530
